org.apache.flink.runtime.event.job

Interface ManagementEvent

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExecutionStateChangeEvent, InputGateProfilingEvent, InstanceProfilingEvent, InstanceSummaryProfilingEvent, OutputGateProfilingEvent, ProfilingEvent, RecentJobEvent, SingleInstanceProfilingEvent, ThreadProfilingEvent, VertexAssignmentEvent, VertexProfilingEvent

    public interface ManagementEvent
    This is a marker interface only. It marks events which should only be accessible via the ExtendedManagementProtocol.
